# What's new June 2021 - Project Operations lite deployment

_Applies To: Lite deployment - deal to proforma invoicing_

Note!

This article applies to Project Operations components with version listed below.

| Project Operations on CDS environment |
| --- |
| 4.11.0.156 |

## Quality updates

| **Feature area** | **Reference number** | **Quality update** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Billing and Pricing | 2281417 | Fixed issue with failing Automatic invoice creation action through invoice schedule |
| Billing and Pricing | 2287835 | Improved Invoice confirmation performance |
| Opportunity Management | 2222555 | Material estimates chargeabily must be correctly copied to Quote line details when using &quot;Import from Project Estimation&quot; function |
| Opportunity Management | 2223427 | Customizations now allowed for GenerateRetainersFromRetainerScheduleOptions action |
| Opportunity Management | 2277528 | Fixed billing milestone value calculation for project contract lines with multiple customers. |
| OProject Planning and Tracking | 2226110 | Fixed intermittent issue with Generate Requirement function in Project team grid. |
| Project Planning and Tracking | 2208109 | Ensure user cannot create a project in one currency but related tasks in another currency |
| Project Planning and Tracking | 2258228 | Updated list of fields allowed to modify with Scheduling entities using Schedule API |
| Project Planning and Tracking | 2293989 | Correct Language and Regional settings must be passed to the project Tasks grid |
| Resource Management | 2220493 | Fixed user experience in the Task grid when quickly marking Resource request as complete |
| Time and Expense | 2194431 | Time entry grid must honor start of the week setting in System settings |
| Time and Expense | 2277311 | Time entry grid: after deleting a cell value cursor now remains in the grid |
